<!-- Notification-bell — spec card render
     Source spec: ds-architect-agent/children/components/feedback.md#notification-bell -->
<div class="dst-component-card">
  <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between mb-2">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900">Notification-bell</h3>
    <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 font-mono">3 variants · 3 sizes · 4 states</p>
  </div>
  <p class="dst-component-intro">Notification indicator anchored at the top-right of the app shell. Pairs with menu / popover for the notification list.</p>

  <div class="dst-spec-row">
    <span class="dst-spec-label">Variants</span>
    <div class="dst-spec-values">
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-variant">default · pure bell</span>
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-variant">withDot · unread indicator</span>
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-variant">withCount · badge with N</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="dst-spec-row">
    <span class="dst-spec-label">Sizes</span>
    <div class="dst-spec-values">
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-size">sm · 32px</span>
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-size">md · 40px</span>
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-size">lg · 48px</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="dst-spec-row">
    <span class="dst-spec-label">States</span>
    <div class="dst-spec-values">
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-state">idle</span>
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-state">hover</span>
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-state">focus</span>
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-state">active · panel open</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="dst-spec-note"><strong>Behavior:</strong> trigger pattern — pairs with menu (action list) or popover (rich panel). <strong>withCount:</strong> shows '99+' if count > 99. <strong>Active:</strong> bell tilt animation on panel open + brand.50 background.</div>
</div>
